# @cardo/tax-cz is published as the @miklik1/cardo-tax-cz GitHub Packages mirror
# (GH Packages requires the npm scope to match the owning user; `cardo` is a taken
# GH username, so the identical artifact ships under @miklik1 and is consumed via a
# `npm:` alias — imports stay `@cardo/tax-cz`). Auth (write:packages token) lives in
# the user-level ~/.npmrc. The alias dies at the M5/M6 monorepo fold-in (→ workspace:*).
@miklik1:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
